# =============================================================================
# GetdressAI — .env намунаси (Vercel ёки маҳаллий npm run dev)
# API калитларни index.html ёки браузерга қўйманг.
# =============================================================================
#
# Тез ўрнатиш — маркетплейс (amazon-paapi + eBay + AliExpress)
# 1) npm install
# 2) Пастдаги калитларни тўлдиринг (намуна):
#    AMAZON_ACCESS_KEY=... AMAZON_SECRET_KEY=... AMAZON_PARTNER_TAG=...
#    EBAY_APP_ID=... EBAY_CERT_ID=... (ихтиёрий EBAY_DEV_ID)
#    ALIEXPRESS_APP_KEY=... ALIEXPRESS_APP_SECRET=... (affiliate учун APP_SIGNATURE + TRACKING_ID)
# 3) Сервер: npm run dev  (= node scripts/dev-server.mjs) → http://127.0.0.1:8787
#
# --- Supabase (логин, профиль, дўкон) ---
# Лойиҳа: https://supabase.com/dashboard/project/rmsluskirebmjxbnebyu → Settings → API
SUPABASE_URL=https://rmsluskirebmjxbnebyu.supabase.co
SUPABASE_ANON_KEY=eyJhbGciOiJIUzI1NiIsInR5cCI6IkpXVCJ9...
#
# Google билан кириш: Supabase Dashboard → Authentication → Providers → Google (OAuth client ID/secret from Google Cloud Console).
# Redirect URLs: маҳаллий http://127.0.0.1:8787/** ва production https://getdressai.com/** (Authentication → URL Configuration).

# --- Premium саҳифаси (public/premium.html) — dressai-api + Stripe.js ---
# dressai-api: npm run dev PORT=3000; CORS: dressai-api .env да ALLOWED_ORIGIN=http://127.0.0.1:8787
# DRESSAI_API_URL=http://127.0.0.1:3000
# Production: DRESSAI_API_URL=https://api.getdressai.com  (dressai-api хостингизга мосланг)

# --- Paddle Billing (public/premium.html) — client-side token + price id ---
# https://developer.paddle.com — Dashboard → Developer tools → client-side token
# PADDLE_CLIENT_SIDE_TOKEN=test_...
# PADDLE_ENVIRONMENT=sandbox
# PADDLE_PRICE_TOPUP_10_USD=pri_...
#
# --- Paddle / браузер checkout учун ochiq URL (dev-server inject) ---
# GETDRESSAI_PUBLIC_ORIGIN ни браузер очадиган база URL қилиб қўйинг (охирида / йўқ).
# injectPremiumHtml() шу URL асосида Paddle.Initialize successUrl / cancelUrl тўлдиради:
#   {ORIGIN}/public/premium.html?paddle=ok
#   {ORIGIN}/public/premium.html?paddle=cancel
# Маҳаллий мисол (npm run dev → 8787):
#   GETDRESSAI_PUBLIC_ORIGIN=http://127.0.0.1:8787
#   → success http://127.0.0.1:8787/public/premium.html?paddle=ok
# Production (намечат доменингиз):
#   GETDRESSAI_PUBLIC_ORIGIN=https://getdressai.com
#   → success https://getdressai.com/public/premium.html?paddle=ok
#
# Paddle Dashboard: Seller → Domains — рухсат: https://getdressai.com
# Webhook: dressai-api POST /billing/paddle-webhook (HTTPS), масалан https://api.getdressai.com/billing/paddle-webhook

# --- AI прокси (/api/outfit) — камида битта йўл ---
# Автомат устунлик: OpenRouter → Groq → OpenAI (охирги булут чора).
# Биттасини мажбурий қилиш: AI_PROVIDER=openrouter|groq|openai|ollama

# OpenAI — одатда охирги вариант: https://platform.openai.com/api-keys
OPENAI_API_KEY=sk-proj-...

# OpenRouter: https://openrouter.ai/keys
# OPENROUTER_API_KEY=sk-or-v1-...

# Groq: https://console.groq.com/keys
# GROQ_API_KEY=gsk_...
# AI_PROVIDER=groq

# Маҳаллий Ollama
# AI_PROVIDER=ollama
# OLLAMA_BASE_URL=http://127.0.0.1:11434

# Ихтиёрий (OpenRouter HTTP-Referer)
# OPENROUTER_SITE_URL=https://getdressai.com
# OPENROUTER_APP_NAME=GetdressAI

# --- Amazon Associates + Product Advertising API (PA-API) ---
# 1) https://affiliate-program.amazon.com — Amazon Associates да рўйхатдан ўтинг.
# 2) Associate Central → Product Advertising API ни ёқинг (талабларни ўқинг).
# 3) AWS IAM ёки PA-API учун Access Key / Secret Key олинг (фақат серверда).
# 4) Partner tag (do‘kon &tag=) — веб search havolalari uchun; dev-server index.html га инъекция:
AMAZON_PARTNER_TAG=yourtag-20
# Сервер томонда каталог/Search (dressai-api ёки keyinroқ route) учун — клиентга чиқмасин:
# AMAZON_ACCESS_KEY=AKIA...
# AMAZON_SECRET_KEY=...
# AMAZON_MARKETPLACE=www.amazon.com
# POST /api/amazon-search — каталог қидирув (amazon-paapi)
# (PA-API калитларни репога қўйманг.)

# --- eBay Developer (OAuth / Browse API — keyin server integratsiya) ---
# 1) https://developer.ebay.com — аккаунт яратинг.
# 2) My Account → Application Keys → Create an App Key (Production ёки Sandbox).
# 3) OAuth учун App ID (Client ID), Cert ID (Client Secret), Dev ID, RuName (redirect URL nomi) керак.
# Барини фақат сервер .env да сақланг (репога коммит қилманг).
EBAY_APP_ID=
EBAY_CERT_ID=
EBAY_DEV_ID=
EBAY_RUNAME=
# POST /api/ebay-search — Browse API (OAuth client_credentials). Ихтиёрий:
# EBAY_USE_SANDBOX=true
# EBAY_MARKETPLACE_ID=EBAY_US
# EBAY_OAUTH_SCOPE=https://api.ebay.com/oauth/api_scope
# EBAY_PRICE_CURRENCY=USD

# --- AliExpress Open Platform (Affiliate product.query — сервердагина) ---
# https://openservice.aliexpress.com — App Key / Secret; affiliate учун App Signature + Tracking ID
# POST /api/aliexpress-search
# ALIEXPRESS_APP_KEY=
# ALIEXPRESS_APP_SECRET=
# ALIEXPRESS_APP_SIGNATURE=
# ALIEXPRESS_TRACKING_ID=
# Ихтиёрий: ALIEXPRESS_SYNC_URL=https://api-sg.aliexpress.com/sync
# POST /api/hybrid-marketplace-search — уч маркетплейс (юқоридаги калитлар)

# --- Хавфсизлик (getdressai dev-server) — иҳтиёрий ---
# GETDRESSAI_MARKETPLACE_API_KEY=...  # ўрнатилса: /api/*-search ва hybrid-marketplace учун Authorization: Bearer ёки X-API-Key
# dressai-api MARKETPLACE_UPSTREAM_API_KEY билан бир хил (прокси сервердан чиқмасин)
# GETDRESSAI_ALLOWED_ORIGIN=https://yourdomain.com  # CORS; бўш = *
# GETDRESSAI_RATE_LIMIT_WINDOW_MS=60000
# GETDRESSAI_RATE_LIMIT_MAX=120
# GETDRESSAI_MARKETPLACE_RATE_LIMIT_MAX=45

# --- Прокси: сўров ҳажми чегараси (токен / нарх назорати) ---
# MAX_CHAT_BODY_CHARS=80000

# --- Hybrid VTON (ixtiyoriy): бошқа originда GPU сервер бўлса, index.html hybridVtonUrl инъекцияси ---
# GETDRESSAI_HYBRID_VTON_URL=https://vton.example.com/api/hybrid-vton
# Маҳаллий: бўш қолдиринг — браузер /api/hybrid-vton (npm run dev) дан фойдаланади.

# =============================================================================
# dressai-api + dressai-app билан тўлиқ улаш (локал стек)
# =============================================================================
# Босқичлар:
#   A) getdressai: npm run dev  →  http://127.0.0.1:8787  (веб + /api/* маркетплейс)
#   B) dressai-api: npm start   →  http://0.0.0.0:3000     (илова API: /image, /auth, /v1/hybrid-…)
#   C) dressai-app: .env да EXPO_PUBLIC_API_URL=http://<сизнинг_LAN_IP>:3000  (Expo Go телефон билан бир Wi‑Fi)
#
# dressai-api .env да getdressai га прокси (бир машинада):
#   HYBRID_MARKETPLACE_UPSTREAM_URL=http://127.0.0.1:8787
#   HYBRID_VTON_SERVICE_URL=http://127.0.0.1:8787          (агар VTON getdressai да бўлса)
# Агар маркетплейс калитлари фақат getdressai .env да бўлса — илова dressai-api орқали чақиради, dressai-api эса 8787 га.
#
# Хавфсизлик (ихтиёрий): GETDRESSAI_MARKETPLACE_API_KEY = dressai-api да MARKETPLACE_UPSTREAM_API_KEY
